translate English day8_b9b08fb1:


    "\n I awake to the sound of crying."


translate English day8_8278b1f6:


    "A girl's crying, endless, sniffling, and hoarse.{w} Next to me, Maya is crying.{w} Did she have another nightmare?"


translate English day8_5142ba51:


    "I fell asleep hugging her, but at some point she must have scooted away; her back is turned."


translate English day8_6df551f9:


    "After realizing what's happening, I don't hug her again. I just hold my breath."


translate English day8_2fbfef2c:


    "It must be morning, because blue light is shining in from the window."


translate English day8_f273e30b:


    "The angel in my dreams...{w} I thought it was Maya, but when I look at her weak back, trembling a little each time a cry escapes her lips..."


translate English day8_c3388010:


    et "I can sense pain and agony--the exact opposite of the angel's constant, calming presence in the dreams."


translate English day8_a5b92ca9:


    my "See you, [na2]."


translate English day8_18ef1d76:


    nar "Despite my morning worries, our parting went smoothly."


translate English day8_28670a8f:


    nar "Maya didn't say any more than that simple goodbye."


translate English day8_ac4be0a5:


    nar "Her words sound more curt than usual.{w} Does she regret having to leave me here like this?"


translate English day8_8060cb8e:


    nar "Naturally, I start to think about our relationship."


translate English day8_0ac6b1c4:


    nar "I guess this means I'm her lover now."


translate English day8_5f6bdafe:


    nar "I always figured that being with someone I love would make me want to jump for joy--or at least feel something out of the ordinary."


translate English day8_6957cbf3:


    nar "Surprisingly, though, I don't feel that much.{w} Is this just what it's like to be someone's lover?"


translate English day8_fab8d230:


    nar "I keep my eyes on her all the way until she disappears from sight, but I never feel my heart leap. I never even feel a hint of loneliness, really."


translate English day8_6b30293f:


    nar "Time passes without leaving room for sentimentality.{w} I'm headed to the Magic Department today per the documents I submitted yesterday."


translate English day8_80a8bbba:


    nar "I chose to go at an early time so as not to draw unwanted attention, but upon going into the bishop's room, there was plenty of that to be had anyway."


translate English day8_76f0206f:


    nar "For some reason, seeing the bishops of the Cleanup Department and Magic Department together doesn't feel real."


translate English day8_b5670ba7:


    nar "So while they have a very serious discussion about me, I lazily think about other things."


translate English day8_a7c87741:


    nar "If I was just gonna be dragged here anyway, I would never have had that fight with Arnie."


translate English day8_40f04c1d:


    nar "Makes it a little hard to face her, you know?"


translate English day8_df47656e:


    hk "Brother [na]."


translate English day8_f1d88acd:


    nar "Eventually, she says my name."


translate English day8_0b172b86:


    hk "Are you sure you don't want to say farewell to the Cleanup Department priests, hmm?"


translate English day8_bf271b5e:


    pl "I'm sure. Just saying goodbye to you is enough."


translate English day8_d21a8148:


    hk "I see..."


translate English day8_58f9e812:


    hk "I had hoped your time with us would be filled with fun, enjoyable memories..."


translate English day8_abeca93a:


    hk "I'm so very sorry that I was unable to give those to you."


translate English day8_fd7ce223:


    nar "When I look up, I see her expression--a little gloomier than usual with a hint of sadness."


translate English day8_e7ded542:


    nar "That causes the reality of the situation to set in a little bit."


translate English day8_fc8610c7:


    pl "No, that's not true at all... And it's not exactly your fault, Bishop."


translate English day8_19787124:


    nar "Upon seeing her, I lower my head again. The smoothness in my words is gone.{w} For some reason, I really don't want to meet her gaze right now."


translate English day8_03a8d4b6:


    er "It's quite clear to me what sort of life you've lived this past week if her last words to you as your boss were an apology."


translate English day8_e901d86a:


    hk "......"


translate English day8_d8fc81ed:


    nar "Bishop Erzsebet says something--I'm not sure if it's an insult or a threat--while he watches our awkward face-to-face, arms folded."


translate English day8_957d268c:


    er "I had wanted to pull you out of this landfill earlier, if possible.{w} It's a tragedy that it had to be after all that's occured."


translate English day8_06329d46:


    er "Getting buried in a place like this is equivalent to death itself."


translate English day8_a92c039c:


    hk "Bishop Erzsebet? {w}I'm sorry to say that your assumption has been built on a foundation of faulty logic."


translate English day8_6416ea01:


    hk "But ever since this department split off from the Magic Department and established itself, literacy rates have improved thanks to basic education."


translate English day8_379dd89f:


    hk "Not only that, but it has resolved the troubles of many a poor sibling isolated from the rest of society..."


translate English day8_6a446d0f:


    er "And thanks to that, what once was a sacred house of worship has become a rotten nest to criminals and dubious ne'er-do-wells in the process."


translate English day8_baa3da22:


    er "I can no longer tell if this is a place for worshipping God or just another prison one would see in back roads.{w} And I heard there's been yet ANOTHER incident."


translate English day8_d44688ef:


    er "Saint Sheol's good name has truly fallen to the ground on its knees."


translate English day8_92b65ade:


    er "You came to this temple with that smug look on your face, putting on airs as if you're king of the proverbial castle."


translate English day8_75ee4bc1:


    er "You're only bishop thanks to your father, who is a far a greater man than you'll ever be."


translate English day8_ad03591f:


    hk "Hm. I will indeed admit that my regulations were lacking in that area...{w} But..."


translate English day8_52e316ff:


    er "But?"


translate English day8_3f80f667:


    hk "Impure accidents like that are exactly why we should all be especially cautious."


translate English day8_b47f561e:


    er "Cautious? Of what?"


translate English day8_d98ce5e8:


    hk "...You may voice as many complaints to me personally as you like, but I am naught but the representative of one department."


translate English day8_1999ae95:


    er "Too confused to respond now that I've said something not in your father's little script?"


translate English day8_bfd5b6d6:


    nar "The air in the room fills with tension."


translate English day8_658d1448:


    nar "In contrast to the Magic Department bishop's scathing criticism, the Cleanup Department bishop stops speaking, as though afraid, and tears up."


translate English day8_867adefa:


    nar "It really pains me to see her like that, but I can't give her any help.{w} I'm not in a position to say thoughtless things right now."


translate English day8_76e74049:


    pl "Still... Thank you for everything, Bishop."


translate English day8_e901d86a_1:


    hk "......"


translate English day8_ec99742f:


    nar "In the end, what came out of my mouth was pretty bland gratitude, but I tell her the words slowly, in time with her breathing."


translate English day8_3f974fb1:


    nar "I wanted to give her the time to calm herself down."


translate English day8_c7f8307c:


    pl "We'll still be in the same building, so we'll see each other around."


translate English day8_afb18757:


    hk "Yes, we will.{w} Please take care of yourself, Brother~"


translate English day8_aa44ae24:


    nar "After bowing to the bishop as she slowly waves to me, I leave the Cleanup Department behind."


translate English day8_e9ad4fd9:


    nar "As I open the door and go through it, the Magic Department bishop stays still for a few moments."


translate English day8_27cd3d67:


    nar "But as I go into the hallway, he suddenly clicks his tongue as if irritated by the dismal atmosphere of the Cleanup Department."


translate English day8_9ef55663:


    nar "To me, the act doesn't seem born purely of a loathing towards filth itself."


translate English day8_fb1b311a:


    er "Eckaran's daughter is always so pathetic.{w} I get goosebumps whenever that duplicitous attitude of hers comes out."


translate English day8_f2fba9ec:


    pl "It seems like you've known our bishop for a pretty long time too, Bishop Eri."


translate English day8_fa8e1f75:


    er "I have, but... It only takes one look at her department to realize how much talent she lacks.{w} And in that sense, the disposal team is the worst of them."


translate English day8_51420b57:


    er "Her assemblage of naive, gullible greenhorns from vulgar birthplaces means she oversees an endless string of disorderly accidents."


translate English day8_23559d96:


    er "Yet while she teaches them, she herself is a mess.{w} Truly a leader of her own kind."


translate English day8_e4624b34:


    er "Your inability to adapt to their department proves you, for one, have your head on straight.{w} There's no need to blame yourself for anything."


translate English day8_f909ab3c:


    nar "It seems like he's choosing his words out of consideration for me, but it still doesn't feel good hearing him talk behind other people's backs."


translate English day8_fd130857:


    nar "And maybe that's because I'm confident in that department, as well as my birthplace.{w} Until just yesterday, I was a part of that very disposal team."


translate English day8_5286615f:


    nar "No matter how you think of it, being appointed an official priest of the Magic Department overnight is an absurd idea."


translate English day8_3d2690d3:


    er "Also... I'm your bishop now.{w} Be more thoughtful of that."


translate English day8_bacfb6bc:


    er "Try not to slip up and act so casual."


translate English day8_d53048e8:


    nar "I hate how his expression keeps getting more and more haughty as we approach his department, but I purposely keep silent."


translate English day8_7673d36b:


    nar "My heart has been whispering to me that I'll just need to get used to things like this from now on."


translate English day8_6820a8b0:


    nar "Standing before the Magic Department priests, the scene is different from the first time I visited the training grounds."


translate English day8_3fd67c87:


    nar "Rather than adopting an aggressive attitude towards me, they welcome me with applause."


translate English day8_4938184c:


    nar "I thought at least a few people would be unhappy about me transferring in like this, but every single one of them gives me a warm welcome."


translate English day8_688f574b:


    nar "Almost like nothing else matters.{w} Maybe it's not that the Magic Department is discriminatory--they just draw a line between their allies and everyone else."


translate English day8_fa7c7f9d:


    nar "The only reason for this sudden change in attitude is my becoming part of this department, and it feels bad.{w} All of them have the same face, the same clothes."


translate English day8_3e5a7fb8:


    nar "I can't even tell who I've said hello to before or who I've had conversations with.{w} Plus, with their black hoods pulled up, it's hard to make out their faces anyway."


translate English day8_c2ac7917:


    nar "Thinking of myself as one of them makes me shudder.{w} No, I've gotta stop that.{w} Nothing's gonna come of me thinking that way right off the bat."


translate English day8_9804e1d9:


    nar "Each of the departments has its own peculiarities.{w} I knew all along the Magic Department was like this, didn't I?"


translate English day8_f483865e:


    nar "I can't piss them off on day one.{w} If my difficulty to adapt gets out, it'll be a repeat of--"


translate English day8_d5802aaf:


    ar "Brother [na2]."


translate English day8_9a033ff0:


    nar "A familiar voice is the first to speak to me in the midst of my dizzying thoughts.{w} It might be my imagination, but it feels like everything else just got a little quieter."


translate English day8_76591f71:


    nar "I look over and awkwardly raise a hand in greeting.{w} I knew this would be awkward for both of us."


translate English day8_112000d2:


    nar "But apparently, for her, it wasn't awkward at all."


translate English day8_edfa044d:


    nar "She'd had to have heard beforehand that I was coming, and yet when she saw me, her face softened into a very happy-looking expression."


translate English day8_4d71c23a:


    nar "In that moment, my earlier mood totally vanishes.{w} Like her, I'm relieved."


translate English day8_0728bfe9:


    nar "But as I slowly lower my hand, I feel a cold sweat break out.{w} Apparently, I'm way more anxious than I thought I'd be."


translate English day8_24f05879:


    pl "Do I need to undo the bandages just so you can measure me?"


translate English day8_f5e60aba:


    ar "If I don't get a proper measurement now, it will only bother you later."


translate English day8_137ff094:


    nar "I had adjusted the temple-provided cassock I originally wore to better fit my size and tastes."


translate English day8_21240fa0:


    nar "But silly vestments like those wouldn't fly in the Magic Department."


translate English day8_83756fba:


    nar "Back in the Cleanup Department, basically everyone modified their clothes to some extent.{w} Apparently, all the other departments see that as a breach of regulation."


translate English day8_e2394058:


    nar "Thanks to the time I spent not caring a bit about regulations, I find myself belatedly surprised."


translate English day8_2cdc6f40:


    pl "Sure, you say that, but...{w} You wouldn't happen to have any ulterior motives, would you?"


translate English day8_c7c2a0bc:


    ar "What sort of ulterior motives could you mean?"


translate English day8_e8f8a767:


    nar "I meant to try and trick her, but as always, she doesn't take the bait.{w} Her reasons for wanting to measure me must really be pure."


translate English day8_a8c2297a:


    pl "Um, never mind.{w} I shouldn't have tried to make a joke like that with you, Arnie."


translate English day8_afe3bd63:


    ar "You've said something similar before...{w} If I've somehow offended you, then I apologize."


translate English day8_ec6542a0:


    ar "I will endeavor to be a little more amenable."


translate English day8_95187624:


    pl "No, I just meant that I'd never be able to win against you."


translate English day8_ab02f2c2:


    nar "Feeling encouraged, I remove the bandages.{w} As expected, her eyes go wide.{w} This is why I didn't want to let her see what was beneath them..."


translate English day8_a86df1a4:


    ar "Brother, I was under the impression your wounds had healed."


translate English day8_9a1f322a:


    pl "Yep, they have.{w} The black marks are just from how they healed. There's no need to worry."


translate English day8_b4eab654:


    ar "They're... fine like that? Truly?"


translate English day8_e918620f:


    pl "I mean, yeah. Do they look weird?"


translate English day8_9a43f72a:


    ar "No, I was just concerned."


translate English day8_4eb91470:


    pl "That's basically the same thing!"


translate English day8_6bd8e88d:


    ar "Is it? I don't think so..."


translate English day8_18152770:


    nar "Arnie takes out a stiff measuring tape, then bends over and puts it under my neck."


translate English day8_005ebf85:


    nar "I see her long eyelashes for just a moment, so close the breath from my nose could brush over them."


translate English day8_7546f714:


    nar "For some reason, that embarrasses me a lot, and I do my best to stop breathing.{w} And that leads me to tighten up my core."


translate English day8_dc451dbe:


    nar "But Arnie gently places a hand on me, as if telling me to relax."


translate English day8_f93c4492:


    nar "It's not awkward or uncomfortable, but it does make my breath catch in my throat.{w} This place is too confined to be in with another person."


translate English day8_ff1b0db4:


    nar "It's a changing room--normally meant for one."


translate English day8_d9a8460c:


    nar "She's focused on sticking close to me and counting off the small numbers, but I can't focus whatsoever."


translate English day8_6a3f7454:


    pl "So, uh, these clothes... When will they be done?"


translate English day8_6190bdd3:


    ar "I'll be ordering them today.{w} They should take around three days."


translate English day8_7c844edf:


    pl "That's vague..."


translate English day8_92d504c5:


    pl "Er, I mean... In the meantime...{w} Are my regular clothes going to make anyone else angry?"


translate English day8_5129534c:


    ar "I can assure you that will never happen.{w} They are all well aware of your circumstances."


translate English day8_f4a6127e:


    ar "Enoch and I wear different clothing from everyone else too, don't we?"


translate English day8_d6761cc9:


    pl "Sure, but that's more like..."


translate English day8_d1baf86a:


    pl "...Never mind."


translate English day8_5e2d0da2:


    ar "Hm...? Well, alright then.{w} If you have anything else to ask of me, please do so, no matter what hour it is."


translate English day8_169269f8:


    nar "There can't be any stenches in the Magic Department room, so when nobody's looking, I bury my nose in my clothes."


translate English day8_6fdefeaf:


    nar "I should have made sure they didn't smell before."


translate English day8_ed5cae3d:


    nar "But they've been properly washed, so they don't smell like they did a few days ago."


translate English day8_0ede54c1:


    nar "Still, maybe I just got used to that unique disposal team stench and others can smell it on me."


translate English day8_77a76c36:


    nar "Why won't anyone say anything about it?{w} Because they know I was part of the disposal team?"


translate English day8_48d2c748:


    nar "All the priests are being weirdly friendly, and it's kind of making me sick."


translate English day8_1f81a039:


    nar "It never would have been like this in the disposal team.{w} Without meaning to, memories of the Cleanup Department flood through my mind."


translate English day8_b558ccf6:


    nar "I didn't think I ever got used to that place--but apparently, I was wrong."


translate English day8_f17640ec:


    ex6 "Umm, Lord [na]?"


translate English day8_508c333b:


    pl "Hm?"


translate English day8_d396d6a1:


    ex6 "Did you understand the explanation? If there's anything you have a question about--"


translate English day8_94665f5e:


    ar "Over there! Is there a problem?"


translate English day8_ad92bd68:


    ex6 "Lady Arne!{w} Well, I was just explaining our duties to our new brother."


translate English day8_4b604ec2:


    ar "I see."


translate English day8_68985373:


    nar "Before she can say any more, I interrupt."


translate English day8_94b83f40:


    pl "Yep, I got it.{w} Thanks so much for explaining!"


translate English day8_3a97151d:


    nar "The priest smiles in relief, then says goodbye to both of us and moves away."


translate English day8_8fade2a9:


    nar "Do the two of us keep ending up alone together because the other priests know about us?"


translate English day8_69030d9c:


    nar "I never really noticed this when passing through, but the training grounds are bigger than I thought."


translate English day8_8b713f2e:


    nar "I hadn't realized at first that the floor was partitioned at all, either, because of the high ceiling."


translate English day8_c6206cae:


    nar "As I thought about it, dizzied by being able to use a facility like this like my own home, Arnie draws up several steps to me."


translate English day8_abc8a746:


    ar "Are you okay?{w} This is your first day here, so you don't need to try and understand too much at once."


translate English day8_fb83e16b:


    pl "Nah, it's fine. I'd get anxious not knowing anything anyway.{w} But is the department really okay with this whole thing? You know, bringing an amateur along for Pestis exterminations..."


translate English day8_6461ebc8:


    ar "But of course--for that which we can see is not everything.{w} You have enough power for it."


translate English day8_e62a5ab9:


    ar "I'm more worried people will ask too much of you and you'll become very busy."


translate English day8_a10098c8:


    pl "Yikes! Don't give me too much work..."


translate English day8_2fb3a106:


    nar "My exaggerated comment must have worked, because Arnie puts the back of her hand to her mouth and laughs softly, showing that the conversation is going smoothly."


translate English day8_66f68e1a:


    nar "With this, she probably won't ever think she'd ruined my mood."


translate English day8_f4c5e392:


    nar "My gaze lazily drifts past Arnie to behind her."


translate English day8_9e5cd230:


    nar "In the densely-packed crowd of priests--they're practically squashed together--I see one person's foot kicking something."


translate English day8_18616833:


    nar "But that something is a head--just a head.{w} Its temple is broken clear open, and it lies in a pool of blood."


translate English day8_24a17f3a:


    nar "I know that corpse disposal isn't the magic department's job, so this must be some sort of Pestis-extermination practice.{w} Nobody seems very surprised as they look at the floor."


translate English day8_2d88dbc9:


    nar "But as I watch, the head's mouth splits off and slowly crawls up the wall."


translate English day8_569ef7d6:


    nar "It then takes root there, flapping its long tongue as if to make fun of the people below."


translate English day8_f8125685:


    nar "Its teeth also chatter with a firm and audible click.{w} It seems to want to attract attention."


translate English day8_29a894df:


    nar "Unfortunately, nobody is really looking at it.{w} The black-robed priests loiter near the pool of blood like corpses announcing death."


translate English day8_c3c74b43:


    pl "Well, that's a strange sight to see."


translate English day8_42a7a34c:


    ar "Strange?"


translate English day8_c81017a0:


    pl "Yeah, that, uh..."


translate English day8_290fee12:


    nar "Her dubious voice repeats the word I used.{w} I avert my eyes and look at her, immediately meeting her gaze."


translate English day8_754c9fda:


    nar "She has her head tilted to the side in mild confusion as she stares at me, eyes gently glowing.{w} As I look at her expression, my face gradually begins to tense up."


translate English day8_45badb9a:


    nar "Anxious, I hurriedly look over there again, but nothing's over there anymore."


translate English day8_908436da:


    ar "Brother...?"


translate English day8_1c809487:


    nar "Hearing her makes my blood run cold.{w} My heart is pounding.{w} I make up an excuse without knowing what my face looks like right now."


translate English day8_1d1e6382:


    nar "I try my best not to avert my eyes from her, but once they begin to wander, everything in front of me gets cloudy."


translate English day8_b15553ba:


    pl "Umm, well..."


translate English day8_da890f5d:


    nar "My voice shakes and my warm, dry breathing gets caught in my throat.{w} Suddenly, a cool hand touches my cheek."


translate English day8_e31f9448:


    nar "My racing heart steadies.{w} Her hand moves up to my temple and massages it, bringing me back to normal."


translate English day8_51cea486:


    nar "I look where she looks, staring at her hand.{w} Her fingertips are covered in lukewarm moisture."


translate English day8_f4369bb4:


    nar "Seeing me at a loss for words, she speaks flatly--with the same expression and tone she always uses."


translate English day8_156f99ab:


    ar "You may want to get some rest."


translate English day8_3a6a35f7:


    nar "I leave the busy training grounds as though sneaking out of them.{w} As my footsteps clap along the silent hallway, I feel the worst I've ever felt."


translate English day8_7984f02c:


    nar "Damn it. Damn it!{w} I curse to myself. I'm going crazy."


translate English day8_090e3a3c:


    nar "No, wait, just going crazy isn't supposed to be this painful.{w} I need to go crazy in a less, well, crazy way."


translate English day8_aa0f7c29:


    nar "Not one good thing has happened today. The whole day has made no sense.{w} Should I just jump off of something and end it all?"


translate English day8_123c7005:


    nar "Ideas I don't actually plan on going through with tumble around in my head.{w} All the negative ideas are emotionally messing me up even more."


translate English day8_05aeee9e:


    nar "I didn't want to surprise Arnie like that.{w} What did she think of me?"


translate English day8_aa40cf33:


    nar "Why is this happening all over again?{w} If the god they believe in really exists, why won't he save me--the one who's actually distressed?"


translate English day8_7bf21a6c:


    nar "I bet the people above the sky are looking down at my suffering and laughing.{w} I say a prayer that's mostly just cursing them."


translate English day8_061bac03:


    nar "The words dance across the tip of my tongue, but they don't come out.{w} Eventually they just turn into outright insults."


translate English day8_6fa2e10b:


    en "Surrounded by people bright and early, huh? Man, you're popular today."


translate English day8_76ce22d0:


    nar "And here's another guy who can't seem to read the room.{w} How can he see me in this state and still say things like that?"


translate English day8_2da572d0:


    pl "Yo, Enoch.{w} Hey, don't tease me too much! Been super busy all morning~"


translate English day8_d1a42d5b:


    en "Haha.{w} So, how are you liking the Magic Department?"


translate English day8_180d23b9:


    pl "That's a pretty dumb question!{w} The room is enormous, the floors are clean, and everyone is even friendlier than I expected."


translate English day8_33d9c066:


    pl "Really puts the other departments to shame!{w} Is it really okay for me to be here?"


translate English day8_523266e8:


    en "Haaah... It's written all over your face, you know.{w} Nobody's telling you to force yourself to act this way. You can relax a little."


translate English day8_b0eed459:


    pl "...Look, I've had a different life than you, Magic Department kid."


translate English day8_3a64e294:


    en "Umm... You know it's not like I've been in this department since I was born, right?"


translate English day8_aab99118:


    en "Don't get me wrong, here.{w} Not everyone with black hair can learn magic like it's nothing."


translate English day8_399629d6:


    pl "Then why the hell am I here?!" with sshake


translate English day8_2d47f5fa:


    en "Look, just take a deep breath..."


translate English day8_cd54d1ee:


    en "It's fine. If you need someone to vent to, you can vent to me all you like."


translate English day8_5cc72646:


    en "But I really want you to get along with Sister and the others. Please?"


translate English day8_385c8a53:


    en "We're one big group, here.{w} If one of us is anxious, it affects everyone."


translate English day8_0a9a7200:


    pl "Oh. Really?{w} And here I thought the Magic Department was bunch of unapologetic elitists."


translate English day8_0f31b4e8:


    en "We don't look down on an individual's abilities, but we do have a tendency to lose our balance if any of our pillars fail."


translate English day8_2d87e134:


    en "That's how important it is for the one at the center of the group to stay unwavering, so..."


translate English day8_f84dfd73:


    en "And I think that's something you can understand, at least a little."


translate English day8_79302aa9:


    nar "Naturally, I understand it well.{w} The bigger the group, the more tight-knit the group, the stronger the one forming its foundation."


translate English day8_d6b94d8d:


    nar "That kind of burden eats away at your life and crushes your humanity.{w} I came here despite hating the idea of belonging to a group like that."


translate English day8_e7de60bb:


    nar "I'm well used to this kind of arrangement--and it makes me sick."


translate English day8_a09862d0:


    pl "Then are you saying I'm a nuisance here?{w} You're pretty narrow-minded, huh? Driving me out is just gonna make Arnie mad, you know."


translate English day8_f3ec558d:


    en "Nuisance? Driving you out? Of course not!{w} I'm saying the opposite, actually."


translate English day8_09c78c58:


    en "We need you here.{w} You came to the Magic Department because we need you."


translate English day8_7e37c811:


    en "So you've gotta at least play nice with us, you know?"


translate English day8_526e825b:


    en "Sister was worried sick, too..."


translate English day8_f4599ec0:


    pl "Wait, is that all you wanted to say to me?{w} I was gonna do that whether you told me to or not."


translate English day8_db26a157:


    pl "In a situation like this, being uncooperative just makes things worse."


translate English day8_bbae1677:


    en "Hmm, yeah, but... Won't that make things really difficult for you, too, [na]?"


translate English day8_23e77a5b:


    en "I may not look it, but I've been pretty worried about you myself..."


translate English day8_264477b9:


    pl "Did she tell you to say that?"


translate English day8_0fab67b5:


    en "No, this is just how I feel."


translate English day8_9dd510b0:


    en "Honestly, I have to say...{w} You're way more on edge than you usually are."


translate English day8_b99baa57:


    en "Do you really hate it here that much?{w} Or is it just the nervousness getting to you?"


translate English day8_79deca3c:


    pl "Hate it here? No, I just..."


translate English day8_6389e7f0:


    pl "I'm just nervous, that's all."


translate English day8_73c2f009:


    nar "Even after Enoch awkwardly departs, I stay here, sitting and looking down at the floor."


translate English day8_ea9d4c3f:


    nar "My feet don't feel uncomfortable because of the pretty carpet here."


translate English day8_5a7c9971:


    nar "I don't see a speck of dirt on the walls and the bathrooms are practically shining--even the mirrors.{w} And as was said before, meals were lavish."


translate English day8_265e001f:


    nar "But most importantly, I'm taking a rest alone while the rest of the Magic Department is busy at work.{w} They're being considerate of the newcomer."


translate English day8_de24486e:


    nar "And I get it.{w} Enoch and Arnie are both really good people, and the Magic Department is actually a wonderful place."


translate English day8_4ef0097e:


    nar "And yet I still can't seem to get used to it."


translate English day8_4bcc550f:


    nar "The system is suffocating.{w} My hair stand on end thinking about what the priests really have on their minds."


translate English day8_5ffcc2eb:


    nar "But when I let my head cool off and really think about it, that's a pretty simple-minded reason."


translate English day8_6868fff5:


    nar "I suddenly question myself.{w} Is that really what's got me feeling so crappy?"


translate English day8_819ae901:


    nar "I haven't been able to calm down since coming here, and I've been weirdly concerned about those around me."


translate English day8_b9017ff3:


    nar "I thought it was just the sense of wrongness, the sense of me not wanting this.{w} But the thing that seems most out of place is me because I can't acclimate to the situation."


translate English day8_2cc10e20:


    nar "I've been averting my eyes from that truth--that's all, plain and simple."


translate English day8_9e59c9ac:


    nar "I slide my hand under my bangs and gently press down on my closed eyes."


translate English day8_c6cb588d:


    nar "A whole bunch of memories flash through my mind, making me dizzy.{w} Why did I come here? What am I here for?"


translate English day8_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day8_18a5e468:


    nar "I muster up breath in my tight chest, then exhale again.{w} I was just about to spiral into self-loathing."


translate English day8_c4cd89c7:


    nar "And that wouldn't help the situation at all."


translate English day8_a766b903:


    nar "If they don't harbor any ill will towards me, that means I shouldn't be anxious, right?"


translate English day8_1b28534d:


    nar "It'll be fine.{w} Like I said before, I was just a little nervous."


translate English day8_404cd8e6:


    nar "I've gotten too used to the irregular lifestyle with the Cleanup Department."


translate English day8_ecec206b:


    nar "I don't ever need to go back there.{w} In fact, I should be relieved."


translate English day8_4d1eca91:


    nar "I continue to take deep breaths as I come up with all those reasons."


translate English day8_ar_a7930371:


    nar "The training grounds were empty, like everyone had snuck out.{w} As I thought, a familiar girl is sitting in the corner of the room."


translate English day8_ar_05eef155:


    nar "I always see her sitting and standing up straight and proud, so it's a little strange seeing her tucked away in a corner like that."


translate English day8_ar_f5fa75d9:


    nar "I go up to her, feeling bad while wondering if she had more work to handle."


translate English day8_ar_0a27dff3:


    nar "As if to put my worries to shame, though, she spots me and immediately rises, giving her clothes a few pats."


translate English day8_ar_9d6e941c:


    ar "Brother [na2]!"


translate English day8_ar_56cdd74d:


    ar "How is your new room?"


translate English day8_ar_87dc5a9b:


    pl "The bed's so big I can't calm down.{w} It's big enough to fit two of me, haha! H-Ha..."


translate English day8_ar_6793328b:


    ar "Hee hee. You always say such funny things."


translate English day8_ar_f12ab63f:


    pl "Are you still working overtime, Arnie?"


translate English day8_ar_9d680518:


    ar "No. I've already finished today's work.{w} It's just..."


translate English day8_ar_6d84050c:


    nar "Arnie uncharacteristically fumbles her answer."


translate English day8_ar_bdea7b28:


    nar "I watch her closely until, a few moments later, she opens her mouth and talks in the same way she always does."


translate English day8_ar_bed459d4:


    ar "Brother, if it's alright with you, would you like to take a short walk with me?"


translate English day8_ar_afae5bc8:


    pl "A walk? Sure thing."


translate English day8_ar_859822d9:


    ar "Thank you so much."


translate English day8_ar_1af85d03:


    nar "She sighs--was she concerned I'd turn her down?{w} She holds out a slender hand to me."


translate English day8_ar_b8ce8713:


    nar "For a moment, I can't return the gesture with my own, which quickly shows my embarrassment."


translate English day8_ar_82b7fe36:


    pl "H-Hey... I'm not a kid, you know."


translate English day8_ar_dc8b1087:


    ar "Is holding hands a childlike act?{w} I learned that it was a basic act in escorting someone."


translate English day8_ar_76467c92:


    pl "Feel like it's backwards.{w} But whatever."


translate English day8_ar_22e0cb86:


    nar "It's not like I've never held her hand before, but her straight fingers, calloused on the joints, feel different from the hand I've held before."


translate English day8_ar_57150eb5:


    nar "It feels both fluid and uniquely strong.{w} And I'd be lying if I said it didn't make me nervous."


translate English day8_ar_7c6a671a:


    nar "I hear her giggle from right next to me."


translate English day8_ar_b12ec8ff:


    ar "Hee hee hee. It's like we're going on a little field trip."


translate English day8_ar_c0c323b7:


    pl "You ARE treating me like a kid...!"


translate English day8_ar_c3ce78d2:


    ar "I apologize. It's been so long since I've had a leisurely walk with someone that it gave my heart a little flutter."


translate English day8_ar_ef0c210f:


    nar "There's nothing much around us to see given we haven't left the temple.{w} On my first day, it was so big I got lost, but now the paths are ingrained in my mind."


translate English day8_ar_4336c7f4:


    nar "She must feel that even more strongly, having been here much longer than me.{w} Why is Arnie so happy, then?"


translate English day8_ar_341c4c8f:


    nar "She only has a friend next to her, and the night air only feels a little brisker."


translate English day8_ar_44472266:


    ar "Are you still uneasy?"


translate English day8_ar_d2ca8b95:


    nar "Her voice becomes calm again, but sounds somehow graver than usual."


translate English day8_ar_c26a43d9:


    ar "You needn't worry. I don't intend to move forward with our engagement without talking to you about it.{w} There's no forcing feelings that were never there to begin with."


translate English day8_ar_b0f57b70:


    ar "I want you to understand that the friendliness we all show you is purely out of goodwill."


translate English day8_ar_2c29744c:


    nar "Unlike me, she once again seems to know exactly what I'm thinking."


translate English day8_ar_0dc13a8d:


    nar "Am I why she looked troubled before we left the training grounds?{w} I feel bad forcing everyone to give me the same talk repeatedly."


translate English day8_ar_f67ebc15:


    pl "Are you really okay with that, though?{w} It won't mess anything up?"


translate English day8_ar_c4462f3c:


    ar "As I've told you, I will manage the entire thing.{w} If that would help you, it would not trouble me in the slightest."


translate English day8_ar_a480f008:


    nar "Once again, I'm doing the same exact thing.{w} She's able to say things that would be rude if said them to her."


translate English day8_ar_b7d6a893:


    nar "But it's not like I was trying to make her do it.{w} I let go of her hand and instead press it to my head, which has started to hurt."


translate English day8_ar_840ffd6e:


    pl "What am I supposed to do now? My mind is a complete mess."


translate English day8_ar_2eac73f6:


    ar "You're hesitating."


translate English day8_ar_71262a91:


    ar "There's no need for you to think about the more complex things, Brother.{w} You can simply focus on gaining knowledge and strength from now on."


translate English day8_ar_1e470be0:


    ar "I'm sure your experiences with us will make you a stronger person."


translate English day8_ar_8332a125:


    pl "You think experiences are important too?"


translate English day8_ar_6daa2f94:


    ar "Yes. I'm only here after so many incidents because of what I've learned.{w} I've never regretted any of it."


translate English day8_ar_b5ed9c24:


    nar "The things she says are nothing if not honest and reliable, and they don't have her usual hesitation.{w} That proves how much she believes in her own perspective."


translate English day8_ar_e00aaa9c:


    pl "You really are incredible. I doubt I'd ever get to be as strong as you..."


translate English day8_ar_b9d147b6:


    ar "I don't think I've come far enough, but if I appear to be a strong person to you, it is likely because I have something to protect."


translate English day8_ar_a1512f59:


    ar "Do you not have something like that, Brother?"


translate English day8_ar_680f172c:


    pl "Something to protect...? Huh, I never really thought about storybook stuff like that."


translate English day8_ar_78b100a3:


    ar "I disagree, for are you not always protecting yourself?"


translate English day8_ar_9d0f48dc:


    ar "Self-preservation is one of our most primal instincts.{w} If you can protect yourself, then I'm sure you can protect other things, and even people, as well."


translate English day8_ar_fd0b4deb:


    nar "She throws out compliments without warning. Now I'm embarrassed."


translate English day8_ar_e2b5ecbb:


    nar "When I meet her sincere gaze, I feel as though I mustn't lie to her anymore, so I make up my mind despite my embarrassment."


translate English day8_ar_1683b79c:


    pl "Well I... I know you might not be the right person to tell this, but there's actually someone I really like."


translate English day8_ar_941ffca2:


    ar "Do you mean... in the sense that you're in love with them?"


translate English day8_ar_9bbee945:


    pl "It's embarrassing to say, but yes."


translate English day8_ar_313c47d4:


    nar "My gaze moves to the side, but I can't even handle that, so I shut my eyes tightly."


translate English day8_ar_9a105717:


    nar "But contrary to all my unease, her next words are unwavering."


translate English day8_ar_38c2ecd2:


    ar "Ah... That truly is good news, then. I'm quite happy to hear it."


translate English day8_ar_89b24c3e:


    pl "Wh-What? Wait, you're actually happy?"


translate English day8_ar_3435dae6:


    ar "Yes, I am. Why do you ask?"


translate English day8_ar_365352e4:


    pl "Well, you're my fiancee, so...?"


translate English day8_ar_aad2ae1d:


    ar "I've certainly treated you as particularly special, but..."


translate English day8_ar_146d7f16:


    ar "I did all that without ever asking you.{w} I've always worried if that was somehow keeping you trapped, Brother."


translate English day8_ar_0e316f44:


    ar "But now you have fallen in love with another.{w} And I feel as happy as if those feelings had happened to me."


translate English day8_ar_13f85aa5:


    nar "She closes her eyes for a moment as if to organize her own thoughts--or to reflect on bygone memories."


translate English day8_ar_66930393:


    nar "The almost excessively dutiful answer she gives me makes me feel like my usual emotions are awkward and clumsy."


translate English day8_ar_1eb66c05:


    nar "That's how indescribable the kindness she feels for me is."


translate English day8_ar_cde61c5a:


    pl "Then if I regret this later..."


translate English day8_ar_e3c3a803:


    ar "What do you mean by regret?"


translate English day8_ar_e75b4393:


    ar "I chose you, and you made this decision.{w} That means that by default, that decision must be the right one."


translate English day8_ar_313c9731:


    nar "How does she never break under pressure?{w} Is it the countless burdens she feels she needs to protect?"


translate English day8_ar_3e0d0466:


    nar "The Magic Department is centered on this person.{w} Thus, she'd have to be strong.{w} And I have entered that group today which was constructed like that."


translate English day8_ar_daf587e5:


    nar "Simply trusting in her and following her instructions would resolve almost all my problems, and all my troubles would feel like they were never really any concern."


translate English day8_ar_dfe761bf:


    nar "How is it even possible she can do that?{w} It's like actual magic."


translate English day8_ar_2acdfde5:


    nar "Thanks to her, now I feel like maybe I can really trust in her and just let my mind empty out."


translate English day8_my_a68345f9:


    nar "Walking along, I arrive at a familiar place. After being somewhere so bizarrely flashy,"


translate English day8_my_6270ca72:


    nar "this place feels more cramped than usual and much shabbier in comparison."


translate English day8_my_f5ece418:


    nar "But Maya loves it here. My eyes pass over the green grass Maya waters everyday and the bench where we engage in everyday chitchat. {w}I like it here, too."


translate English day8_my_3fc50c3a:


    nar "I wonder what Maya was up to today? {w}Who did she talk to and what did she spend her time doing?"


translate English day8_my_c981e606:


    nar "Maya must have suffered alone, just like I did. I can still see her, even when I close my eyes."


translate English day8_my_4dc3b221:


    nar "It was then that she miraculously appears before me, heralded by her quiet footsteps."


translate English day8_my_a21bdf76:


    my "[na2]? What are you doing here?"


translate English day8_my_5261c5ed:


    pl "I guess I was hoping to see you..."


translate English day8_my_d4f646c1:


    nar "Caught off guard by her sudden appearance, I blurt out the truth before heaving a huge sigh in my mind."


translate English day8_my_ac069fb0:


    nar "I wish I could've come up with a cooler sounding line! {w}I quickly change the topic before I can feel more embarrassed."


translate English day8_my_069d3ff4:


    pl "How was work today? Everything go well?"


translate English day8_my_52cefb03:


    my "Yes, everyone was very helpful..."


translate English day8_my_0d780e83:


    nar "She says before clamping her mouth shut and averting her gaze. {w}Unable to find something to say in response, we both fall silent."


translate English day8_my_eacdb918:


    nar "Were things between us always like this? {w}We've only been apart for one day and yet I feel this indescribable distance between us."


translate English day8_my_b8b99880:


    nar "Perhaps finding the silence just as uncomfortable as I do, Maya speaks up first to break the tension between us while keeping her gaze averted."


translate English day8_my_2ea1f48e:


    my "What about you, [na2]?"


translate English day8_my_67967640:


    pl "Everything went well. I haven't really learned much about the job yet, but with a name like the Magic Department, it's not like it's a secret."


translate English day8_my_23855720:


    pl "Have you been to any of the big buildings yet around here?"


translate English day8_my_09f67c44:


    my "Mm-hm."


translate English day8_my_91cff488:


    pl "Those all belong to the Magic Department. I was really surprised the first time I went inside! {w}They're almost the same size as the temple itself, but the whole building belongs to the department."


translate English day8_my_7ceb58c8:


    pl "Actually, part of the reason it's so big is because there are dorms on the third floor."


translate English day8_my_19fff942:


    pl "Even the rooms are incredibly spacious! I'll have to show you around sometime."


translate English day8_my_3192a791:


    my "That's neat. Though I'm sure I won't be allowed in since I'm not part of that department."


translate English day8_my_e5c91474:


    pl "Oh, you think so?"


translate English day8_my_7e3885b8:


    pl "Ah... Oh! I met a really kind sister and brother, Arne and Enoch. They're pretty famous around here, so I was wondering if you knew them?"


translate English day8_my_443bac56:


    pl "They're both auxiliary bishops for the Magic Department, so I'm sure if I asked them nicely, they'd make an exception... If it's okay with you, of course."


translate English day8_my_a0a9dbae:


    nar "That's where our conversation breaks off. {w}Maya doesn't give me an immediate reply, meaning all I can do is stand there with my mouth shut, waiting for her to say something."


translate English day8_my_2b777d31:


    my "You're amazing, [na2]. {w}From what you've told me, it sounds like fun. {w}Thank you for sharing."


translate English day8_my_8b33acf3:


    nar "But the silence doesn't last long. {w}I'd worried that I committed some kind of verbal slip, but her reply, as kind as always, fills me with relief."


translate English day8_my_c299bb6c:


    pl "It makes me happy to hear you say that!"


translate English day8_my_df7b1ad2:


    my "Well, I should get going. {w}I just stopped by to look at the buds before going to sleep."


translate English day8_my_bcf4b6b1:


    pl "Oh, yeah? I'm sorry for bothering you when you're probably exhausted."


translate English day8_my_49f974fd:


    my "It's fine. Also..."


translate English day8_my_ba156ca8:


    my "I honestly just happened to stop by today, so don't bother coming all the way out here tomorrow. {w}You're still a new recruit, [na2], and I'm sure you're busy."


translate English day8_my_fd2bc761:


    pl "I'm sorry for bothering you, Maya... I never planned on abandoning you. I mean it. {w}I should come see you more often..."


translate English day8_my_378f2e70:


    my "Don't worry. I'm okay. I don't think that way at all. Really."


translate English day8_my_f104c0c4:


    pl "The way back is pretty dark, right? Want me to at least walk you to the dorms?"


translate English day8_my_61b254f7:


    my "No, I'll be okay. Besides, it's not that far. {w}See you around, [na2]."


translate English day8_my_e79b8230:


    nar "As she walks off without looking back, her small body looks like the one I saw this morning."


translate English day8_my_a63b5c45:


    nar "A short goodbye that felt curt and cold. It's as if she's distancing herself from me."


translate English day8_my_41069c6c:


    nar "Although Maya didn't say so out loud, I can tell she's moody about me having moved to a different department."


translate English day8_my_52c2c082:


    nar "If I really do like her, then I should try to be more sensitive toward her very valid emotions."


translate English day8_my_6686e746:


    nar "Though we're only separated by physical distance, I feel like she's grown emotionally distant from me as well."


translate English day8_my_3fb06a17:


    nar "It makes me lonely--a sentiment I didn't feel this morning."


translate English day8_night_6bbae789:


    nar "...The sky is already pitch-black."


translate English day8_hakuB_996147e7:


    nar "This road seems familiar. I remember passing down it on my first day here."


translate English day8_hakuB_5f49d6cb:


    nar "Overgrown vegetation, weeds that have grown ankle-high next to unfamiliar flowers. {w}It might just be me, but the polar night seems darker than normal."


translate English day8_hakuB_9cb1bc8c:


    nar "I didn't notice it the first time I came here, but there is a \"No Entrance\" sign, just as the bishop mentioned. {w}It's set back a bit from the road itself."


translate English day8_hakuB_dbeda055:


    nar "The grass that grows wild within the woods, damp from the recent rain, seems to look more alive and vibrant the deeper you go, while at the same time exuding a slightly strange scent."


translate English day8_hakuB_5896fa45:


    nar "It reeks almost like rotting food. The stench of human flesh mixes with soil, turning it into mud."


translate English day8_hakuB_01ced6ae:


    nar "Breathing it in leaves me increasingly anxious and irritable, my heart hammering away a mile a minute."


translate English day8_hakuB_08c6837d:


    nar "I've been looking forward to meeting her again here."


translate English day8_hakuB_60a6b4d2:


    nar "She stands alone, dominating the space around her, bathed in a pure white light underneath the dark sky."


translate English day8_hakuB_94e8ea41:


    hk "An unexpected guest."


translate English day8_hakuB_3b994280:


    pl "I didn't think you'd be here, either, Your Excellency."


translate English day8_hakuB_e8e9d02f:


    hk "Ah, didn't you come here expecting to see me?"


translate English day8_hakuB_bba1cae1:


    nar "I can't hide it so easily this time. Sharply intelligent eyes hidden beneath a white veil watch me closely."


translate English day8_hakuB_f59ae432:


    nar "It's a fairly indifferent response, but I have to muster all the strength I can to calm my quivering soul."


translate English day8_hakuB_158ea00b:


    pl "You're right, I did come here to see you."


translate English day8_hakuB_c2e0c06c:


    hk "Hmm..."


translate English day8_hakuB_a7969f5d:


    hkn "Well, this won't do..."


translate English day8_hakuB_8fba4a7f:


    nar "She says, her movements elegant and flowing."


translate English day8_hakuB_94c02a8b:


    nar "She leaves a path of broken stalks and crushed flowers behind her, her head bowed reverently low."


translate English day8_hakuB_8aa2154f:


    nar "She almost looks like a royalist, bowing down in utter respect before her liege."


translate English day8_hakuB_5039e304:


    hkn "This area is off limits. {w}There should have been a sign informing you of such."


translate English day8_hakuB_83561c5e:


    pl "You already told me that."


translate English day8_hakuB_aa7bc06d:


    hkn "So why haven't you returned to the dorms yet?"


translate English day8_hakuB_77ec7e53:


    pl "To tell you the truth, I got lost. I was drawn here by the smell of corruption."


translate English day8_hakuB_d549d077:


    hkn "Beyond this chapel lies a pit used to dispose of garbage."


translate English day8_hakuB_d0341d17:


    hkn "The overflow of food and drink we cannot accommodate ourselves along with remnants of Pestis are shoved into this hole where we wait for it to be returned to the soil."


translate English day8_hakuB_38f47577:


    hkn "That accounts for the corrupt smell you mentioned, which is why entrance to this area is strictly forbidden... {w}I'm sorry I hadn't offered a better explanation before."


translate English day8_hakuB_38f4026e:


    pl "I see. This is the first I'm hearing of it. {w}That still doesn't explain what you're doing here at this time of night, though."


translate English day8_hakuB_641335ce:


    hkn "As the bishop of the Cleanup Department, it is my duty to guide lost, wretched believers such as yourself back onto the path."


translate English day8_hakuB_1e4b664a:


    pl "Even though I'm a member of the Magic Department now?"


translate English day8_hakuB_78dbf7d7:


    hkn "Oh, did that already take place?"


translate English day8_hakuB_82392a9a:


    pl "This morning. You were with me, in fact."


translate English day8_hakuB_c542b399:


    hkn "Alas, I cannot be expected to remember everything that happens in a day, being as busy as I am. {w}Especially regarding a priest who has left my flock."


translate English day8_hakuB_9f9a9165:


    pl "That's not what you told me before."


translate English day8_hakuB_d220baa9:


    "\n \"Insolent brat. Hush thyself.\""


translate English day8_hakuB_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_hakuB_41c7f063:


    "\n The unfamiliar voice snaps me back to reality."


translate English day8_hakuB_8d9da76c:


    "Her white veil slips from her head, exposing her tousled hair underneath. {w}Each delicate strand is bathed in moonlight, glittering like grains of glass."


translate English day8_hakuB_16305198:


    "Without the veil in the way, her eyes shine so brightly that I find myself frozen in place, unable to move."


translate English day8_hakuB_b74fd16d:


    "I suppress the sob that threatens to spill from my lips as I stare back at her."


translate English day8_hakuB_53bccbb7:


    et "This time I'm sure of it. She's the one I've been looking for."


translate English day8_hakuB_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_hakuB_cd4bc4ff:


    hk_bq "Why were you looking for me?"


translate English day8_hakuB_a36a90de:


    pl "I just figured you'd be here."


translate English day8_hakuB_ea3ed22a:


    nar "She exhales loudly, as if fed up by my answer. The sneer on her face is impossible to ignore."


translate English day8_hakuB_083ca562:


    hk_bq "Hah! Brocade retains its elegance, even when reduced to rags. It is still a thing of magic, albeit unsuited for your body."


translate English day8_hakuB_7b32ab09:


    hk_bq "I know about the old geezer's efforts... {w}but what he's brought this time is quite intriguing."


translate English day8_hakuB_21d1e3ab:


    nar "I don't quite understand everything she's saying, but I know enough to quickly understand that she's insulting me."


translate English day8_hakuB_e9badc81:


    nar "Her rude manner of talking mixed with raucous laughter, her sarcastic attitude, and all of it emphasized by her cold, blue stare."


translate English day8_hakuB_eb4338b9:


    nar "By 'geezer,' did she mean the bishop Erzsebet? {w}It's hard to believe this woman is the same one I saw this morning."


translate English day8_hakuB_3087c037:


    nar "This woman standing before me with the all too familiar face is nothing like the one I know."


translate English day8_hakuB_150f8133:


    pl "Who are you?"


translate English day8_hakuB_097563c8:


    hk_bq "The one you've been seeking."


translate English day8_hakuB_1d3babee:


    pl "You seem to be in a pretty bad mood."


translate English day8_hakuB_45068e22:


    hk_bq "Sorry, but I hate when people waste my time."


translate English day8_hakuB_94ff326f:


    nar "The corners of her mouth twitch involuntarily. {w}It must be a tic she develops when irritated."


translate English day8_hakuB_4273ad0e:


    nar "It transforms her face into a ridiculous mask, something she seems to be well aware of."


translate English day8_hakuB_9a8bc6a6:


    pl "I really hope this isn't the case of the curious cat making a huge mistake."


translate English day8_hakuB_3f89463d:


    hk_bq "Your attitude has remained a consistent problem, and you must be taught to heel and obey."


translate English day8_hakuB_5c53dbd9:


    nar "Cold sweat runs down the sides of my throat when I hear her cruel voice. {w}Pure malice--that much is abundantly clear."


translate English day8_hakuB_5ae344b3:


    nar "Rationally speaking, there's no real reason for this sudden burst of hostility toward me. And yet alarm bells are going off inside my head. {w} Their ringing is telling me to run."


translate English day8_hakuB_253b943a:


    nar "She doesn't really need a reason to attack me. Kind of like... {w}A wild beast who might tear a human to shreds."


translate English day8_hakuB_401eb905:


    nar "My hyperalert senses take in every minute expression, catches every time she clears her throat, hears every breath she takes, which only helps me make up my mind."


translate English day8_hakuB_650c3684:


    nar "The tension between us is palpable."


translate English day8_hakuB_6bb2b0a7:


    nar "My blood-filled brain works overtime as I realize I need to get out of this situation."


translate English day8_hakuB_1a1860a7:


    pl "I have no idea what you're planning on doing, but you shouldn't do whatever you're thinking."


translate English day8_hakuB_e1d725f7:


    hk_bq "Really now?"


translate English day8_hakuB_e0af4193:


    pl "I'm a member of the Magic Department as of today. So you must know that means I'm under the protection and care of Bishop Eri, right?"


translate English day8_hakuB_5e83a819:


    pl "If you try anything funny, you won't get away with it, no matter how well you disguise yourself to look like Haku."


translate English day8_hakuB_1e3d4ccd:


    hk_bq "Hmm..."


translate English day8_hakuB_84c9660e:


    pl "I see you sneaking around every night. Your grand entrances upon your return don't help, either..."


translate English day8_hakuB_d546fc85:


    pl "I have no idea what you're doing here, but you're clearly trying to stall me for some reason."


translate English day8_hakuB_7b0b3795:


    pl "Leading me to believe you don't want anyone to know about this place."


translate English day8_hakuB_7e4ce2aa:


    nar "But this creature in front of me is not a ravenous beast. She's taken the form of a person, using human language I can understand."


translate English day8_hakuB_ebfbd1ea:


    nar "If she really is human, then I might be able to come up with a way to make an escape."


translate English day8_hakuB_c99c547a:


    pl "I'll let you off the hook today as long as you tell me what you were planning."


translate English day8_hakuB_40bf5cdd:


    nar "It doesn't take me long to realize how overly naive my thought process was. {w}The sound of her hoarse laughter causes my entire body to stiffen."


translate English day8_hakuB_d0569c7a:


    hk_bq "Hahaha!!! I've had enough of your arrogant behavior! To think you'd use some toothless geezer's name, a man with his foot already in the grave, to threaten ME!" with sshake


translate English day8_hakuB_1ace7e0c:


    pl "His foot in the... what now?"


translate English day8_hakuB_214f260f:


    hk_bq "This so-called bishop, who you seem to suck up to like candy, will have his head sliced from his body before the day is done."


translate English day8_hakuB_ebee3f75:


    hk_bq "You sought me out just to babble this nonsense at me? {w}You're as brave as you are ignorant."


translate English day8_hakuB_a921663c:


    hk_bq "This courage you seem to possess is rather commendable,"


translate English day8_hakuB_6f58c68f:


    hk_bq "but don't bark quite so loud. It exposes the fear underneath it all."


translate English day8_hakuB_eb1e660c:


    pl "..."


translate English day8_hakuB_332b6ac8:


    hk_bq "There was a young girl who confronted me once, shouting similar threats... {w}Energetic young things are my favorite!"


translate English day8_hakuB_d71c2d06:


    hk_bq "Which is why I despise brats like you!"


translate English day8_hakuB_1a0557b6:


    nar "She kicks at the dirt with the heel of her boot to show her annoyance,"


translate English day8_hakuB_791abd3d:


    nar "and then, as if remembering something, she laughs while raising a hand to her brow."


translate English day8_hakuB_371abd93:


    nar "She speaks in a voice much deeper than usual. {w}How is it possible to look like the spitting image of someone and yet be so different?"


translate English day8_hakuB_01e508cd:


    hk_bq "Since you're here, I think you deserve a reward of sorts. I'll let you in on a little secret."


translate English day8_hakuB_77c6a3fb:


    hk_bq "Have you ever heard of a person being returned to God?"


translate English day8_hakuB_5af21401:


    nar "I'm not sure what happens here in the capital, but where I come from, it's customary to not hold a funeral for anyone who dies past the age of seven."


translate English day8_hakuB_22868d00:


    nar "Stigmata tend to manifest around the age of eight, so if a child dies before they receive one, we believe they return to Heaven"


translate English day8_hakuB_b2603511:


    nar "without receiving the saving graces of God."


translate English day8_hakuB_162e94c4:


    nar "The land beneath us grows increasingly rotten, leading to a higher childhood mortality, and so this is the story we tell ourselves to make us feel better about our lack of control."


translate English day8_hakuB_86903739:


    pl "You mean the stuff about how we are all children of God until seven years old?"


translate English day8_hakuB_bf6443f1:


    hk_bq "Close, but no."


translate English day8_hakuB_39112405:


    nar "She glances off to the side before lightly clearing her throat."


translate English day8_hakuB_89d27fe7:


    nar "I try to discretely figure out what she's looking at but all I find is nothing more than a dark forest road."


translate English day8_hakuB_600161fd:


    hk_bq "God is far greedier than you might think. {w}And fate is far from fair."


translate English day8_hakuB_29a33371:


    hk_bq "He has no problem taking everything you felt was rightfully yours before you even have time to register what's happening."


translate English day8_hakuB_97e68d2a:


    hk_bq "And this isn't something that will happen in the distant future. {w}You are all too busy rejoicing and being merry to notice your own eternal damnation is right beneath your ignorant noses."


translate English day8_hakuB_e3f3cbbb:


    nar "She continues her violent diatribe without pause to make sure I'm following."


translate English day8_hakuB_6cf8aeed:


    nar "One word in particular from her flood of vitriol seems to stab straight into my brain."


translate English day8_hakuB_3cf64f9d:


    pl "What was that about eternal damnation?"


translate English day8_hakuB_d051e319:


    hk_bq "What you zealots so conveniently refer to as Pestis..."


translate English day8_hakuB_b5c01100:


    pl "Hang on, what's going to happen to us?"


translate English day8_hakuB_e9bd90a0:


    hk_bq "Those of us who can no longer stay between Heaven and Earth shall return whence we came."


translate English day8_hakuB_c474e0b9:


    nar "She rolls up her sleeve, sticks up her index finger, and points it straight at the sky above us."


translate English day8_hakuB_39bc84c4:


    hk_bq "After all is said and done, we all return to God."


translate English day8_hakuB_82f9d377:


    nar "This outrageous act of mimicry is her transparent attempt at mocking me for some of the blasphemous things I've said in the past."


translate English day8_hakuB_b1a83b43:


    hk "Once the sacrifices have been made, everything will go according to our Father's plan. {w}I'm sure I've dumbed it down so even someone like *you* can understand."


translate English day8_hakuB_7d3673fe:


    nar "Father? Do you mean your actual father, the cardinal of the temple? Or are you talking about...?"


translate English day8_hakuB_4944135c:


    nar "As I struggle through my brain fog, I suddenly remember a verse I heard once."


translate English day8_hakuB_1281095a:


    nar "The spirit of the Lord is upon me. {w}For he has anointed me to proclaim good news to the poor."


translate English day8_hakuB_9e7acbc8:


    nar "He has sent me to proclaim good news to the downtrodden and destitute. To proclaim freedom for the prisoners and recovery of sight for the blind."


translate English day8_hakuB_7b044d20:


    nar "To set the oppressed free. The time of the Lord's Favor has come."


translate English day8_hakuB_ba2f64f1:


    nar "Without donning this human-made figure, she is unable to be graced by the blessing of salvation."


translate English day8_hakuB_4e850bad:


    nar "For only by wearing this suit of flesh can she command those around her to follow her,"


translate English day8_hakuB_9bc758f9:


    nar "and so she becomes flesh in order to dwell among us. {w}And we are blessed by her glory."


translate English day8_hakuB_1f4fc5f7:


    nar "The same glory bestowed upon our Father's own son, full of verity and grace."


translate English day8_hakuB_a1c99058:


    nar "...But her very existence denies the existence of God."


translate English day8_hakuB_b61f8ade:


    nar "If what she says is true and God has lent her a body so she might descend to earth and save humanity, {w}then her words about the destruction of mankind means she is the embodiment of Pestis."


translate English day8_hakuB_d99c505e:


    nar "She is Pestis, decked out in a loaner flesh and blood body for her descent to earth. {w}But why did she come here?"


translate English day8_hakuB_dea6b99a:


    nar "With my head full of convoluted thoughts that shoot through my mind, one after the other, I open my parched mouth to speak, convinced of one simple fact."


translate English day8_hakuB_7190b353:


    pl "This must mean you're not human!"


translate English day8_hakuB_0fc67d7d:


    hk_bq "That's a rude remark to say to a lady!"


translate English day8_hakuB_18af6a4d:


    pl "What was that talk about Erzsebet dying?"


translate English day8_hakuB_69e1dd80:


    hk_bq "Did I not mention that the wrath of God himself is upon us? {w}His death alongside is merely a... pleasant perk."


translate English day8_hakuB_60991410:


    hk_bq "We'll start with the emperor of the Magic Department's daughter, that peculiar monk mage, {w}and throw in those ancient temple elders who somehow seem to avoid death, clinging to their useless reign for far too long."


translate English day8_hakuB_42c8ec01:


    hk_bq "Depending on what happens, perhaps even some of my feeble lambs and that girl you like so much will return with me to the beginning of the world, {w}to rejoin their mothers from whence they came."


translate English day8_hakuB_3528d569:


    hk_bq "And if you try anything stupid, you will find yourself suffering a similar fate. Understand?"


translate English day8_hakuB_a126d5bf:


    pl "So you're saying sacrificing a human life is worth saving ourselves from eternal damnation?"


translate English day8_hakuB_21f69ce6:


    hk_bq "This is the true reason why this woman exists."


translate English day8_hakuB_20cd57ff:


    nar "She grips the hem of her skirt in both hands, her sleeves rolled up to the elbows, before giving a slight curtsy in my direction."


translate English day8_hakuB_ab545f54:


    nar "As she slowly opens her eyelids once more, I can clearly see the sneer of disgust on her face, {w}illuminated in the darkness by the glow from her eyes."


translate English day8_hakuB_baab317e:


    nar "The gesture was nothing more than a mockery of human etiquette, with not even a hint of elegance or modesty. {w}Only contempt for this woman she pretends to be."


translate English day8_hakuB_ded74d23:


    pl "The bishop would have never wanted this!" with sshake


translate English day8_hakuB_f5fd0350:


    hk_bq "Your undying support for her is something I truly envy."


translate English day8_hakuB_40cc33fb:


    nar "I'm gradually losing my temper. {w}Since the first time I stood before Pestis, nothing they've said has made any sense."


translate English day8_hakuB_99e6fcc2:


    nar "All I can do is stand here while they crush me with their contemptuous words and actions."


translate English day8_hakuB_7e2a59fe:


    nar "But I can't hold back any longer. {w}All I want in this moment is to scream at the top of my lungs, even if it means being ripped to shreds by this ferocious beast."


translate English day8_hakuB_cce99ef3:


    hk_bq "I hope that's enough to satisfy that seemingly insatiable curiosity of yours."


translate English day8_hakuB_fe7a6bb0:


    nar "She creeps closer to me, step by step. {w}I find myself backing away as she does so, realizing too late she has me trapped."


translate English day8_hakuB_a55f00e4:


    nar "Despite there being a clear avenue of escape behind me with no obstacles in my way, {w}I realize now she had me the moment I stepped foot into this place."


translate English day8_hakuB_4919c0f5:


    nar "Which is why there's no point in running. {w}I have no idea what to do."


translate English day8_hakuB_4a144a25:


    hk_bq "So... what is your plan now?"


translate English day8_hakuB_e2c9a8e5:


    hk_bq "I hope you don't intend to beg me for your life and the lives of those around you?"


translate English day8_hakuB_10294e2c:


    pl "How dare you try and make light of this..."


translate English day8_hakuB_832d392f:


    hk_bq "Only time will tell who is the fool here."


translate English day8_hakuB_4504145f:


    pl "I won't let you get away with this!"


translate English day8_hakuB_185a00ee:


    hk_bq "Foolish boy..."


