    nar "Just then, I feel something touch me just below my neck. {w}Human fingers. {w}By the time I realize what's happening, she already has a firm grip around my throat." with sshake


translate English day8_hakuB_11c95c24:


    nar "Her hands feel almost unnaturally cold thanks to the gloves she always wears, and it's not long before I find myself unable to breath."


translate English day8_hakuB_f708c9c0:


    nar "I try to scream, my eyes open wide in shock, but with her hand around my neck, I can't make a sound."


translate English day8_hakuB_10685a7d:


    nar "All I can see through my distorted vision is the owner of that hand, her face unnaturally calm."


translate English day8_hakuB_b3b42e18:


    nar "A vividly cool voice slips inside my ears, the words etching themselves into my brain."


translate English day8_hakuB_4004ac42:


    hk_bq "If you come here again, seeking out a being you do not truly understand,"


translate English day8_hakuB_4039d595:


    hk_bq "you will die. Not by the hands of God, but by the power of Pestis itself."


translate English day8_hakuB_3d2cee33:


    nar "The moment she finishes speaking, the pressure on my throat vanishes, and I crumple to the ground." with sshake


translate English day8_hakuB_8883c5d6:


    nar "The weed-ridden ground is soaked with rainwater. {w}My clothes and face are instantly coated in mud."


translate English day8_hakuB_4e4bcca5:


    nar "I struggle to see through the wet bangs that slipped over my face, obscuring my vision, {w}but I can't make her figure out."


translate English day8_hakuB_84790728:


    nar "My back and the shoulder that hit the ground when I fell throb with dull pain. {w}I guess this is what it means to hit rock bottom."


translate English day8_hakuB_742b0132:


    hk_bq "Get out of my sight. {w}You are not welcome here, boy."


translate English day8_hakuB_ee0dbaa0:


    nar "And with those parting words, she vanishes from my line of sight. {w}I hear the sound of a heavy door somewhere nearby open and then shut."


translate English day8_hakuB_01978594:


    nar "She must have keys to the chapel. Everything feels like a dream, aside from the pain which is vividly real."


translate English day8_hakuB_2c5d299b:


    nar "I get to my feet, dusting myself off as best I can before running off, leaving those woods behind me."


